  SynosCD -->|Manage only labeled resources| ACA3
  SynosCD -->|Resolve secret refs| KV

  TF -->|Creates/updates| ACE
  TF -->|Deploys bootstrap app| SynosCD

  SynosCLI[synos CLI] -->|diff/sync/status| SynosCD
